{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"1. El (Día) del Gran Sobresalto[1178].","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1178]  Este es uno de los nombres que recibe el Día de la Resurrección, y recibe este nombre porque los corazones de la gente se sobresaltarán, aterrados por el horror que observarán.","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:2","price":"2. ¿Qué es el (Día) del Gran Sobresalto?","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:3","price":"3. ¿Sabes qué es realmente el (Día) del Gran Sobresalto?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:4","price":"4. Es el día en que la gente parecerá mariposas dispersas (debido a la confusión del momento),","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:5","price":"5. y las montañas parecerán lana cardada (hasta que se desvanezcan).","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:6","price":"6. En cuanto a aquel cuyas (buenas) obras pesen más (que las malas) en la balanza ","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:7","price":"7. gozará de una vida placentera (en el paraíso);","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:8","price":"8. mientras que aquel cuyas buenas obras pesen menos (que las malas) en la balanza ","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:9","price":"9. caerá de cabeza al abismo (del infierno).","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6166,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:10","price":"10. ¿Y sabes qué es el abismo (del infierno)?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6167,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"101:11","price":"11. Es un fuego abrasador.","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6168,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"}],"chapter":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah","Chapter Al-Qari'ah","Qari'ah","Surah Qari'ah","Chapter Qari'ah","Al Qari'ah","Surah Al Qari'ah","Chapter Al Qari'ah","Surah 101","Chapter 101","The Calamity","القارعة"]}